    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/seed137-test-performance",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Neural network test-set performance — seed 137",
      "description": "Training run with random seed 137 achieved MAE = 0.0031 RH units and R² = 0.9928 on the same held-out test set. Worst-case RH operating point correctly ranked in top 2 of 5 flow-speed combinations. The package notes that both seed runs 'agree closely' and treats this as confirmation of model stability. No statistical bounds on seed-to-seed prediction spread, no ensemble variance, and no UQ characterization of the magnitude or clinical significance of inter-seed disagreement are provided."
    },
