      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Neural network training code version-controlled; inference pipeline validated against reference CFD outputs within 1% tolerance.",
      "rationale": "PyTorch v2.1 training scripts stored in institutional GitLab repository with tagged release v2.1.3. Automated unit tests cover data normalization, forward-pass dimensions, and loss convergence. Inference pipeline independently verified by a second analyst against 20 reference CFD cases; all predictions within 0.8% of CFD-derived RH values."
    },
