      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is the primary quantity specified in the 510(k) submission pathway for CPB devices. The neural network is trained to predict RH directly from operating conditions and geometric tolerance parameters, eliminating intermediate quantity mapping. Clinical relevance confirmed by clinical engineer review."
    },
    {
